Type: Package
Package: analyticaid
Title: Automated Data Cleaning and Analysis for ODK and Kobo Datasets
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Md Mehedi Hasan", "Khan", 
           email = "plannermehedi@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: analyticaid automates data cleaning, validation, and analysis 
    workflows for survey data collected via ODK and Kobo. It provides streamlined 
    functions for audit log reading, duration analysis, variable collapsing, and 
    automated checks, helping users process and analyse field data quickly and 
    consistently.
